De_battleship (build 50 )						
By Bluestrike http://www.bluestrike.be

Map supports up to 64 players


Briefing:
------------

Training mission,Red squad plays the terrorists who have to plant a bomb
on this battleship.
Blue team plays the CT Unit.
Loosing team pays for the drinks in the bar.
